  "text": "The need for inverse of the Jacobian in the dynamic formulation comes from the derivation of the Λ, µ, and p matrices. These are the pseudo kinetic energy, Coriolis, and Centrifugal matrices in task space, and were all derived from the joint space equivalent. They are derived in [CITATION_1] and [10] as the following:",
